<FAWindow>:
    txt1:txt1
    txt2:txt2
    
    FloatLayout:
        Button:
            pos_hint:{"x":0.01, "top":0.988}
            id:btn
            background_normal: "green.png"
            text: 'FA'
            on_release: dropdown.open(self)
            size_hint:0.15, 0.15

        Widget:
            on_parent: dropdown.dismiss()
            
        DropDown:
            id: dropdown
            on_select:btn.text='{}'.format(args[1])
            Button:
                text:'DFA'
                size_hint_y: None
                
                on_release:
                    dropdown.select('DFA')
                    root.df()
            Button:
                text:'NFA'
                size_hint_y: None
                
                on_release:
                    dropdown.select('NFA')
                    root.nf()
                    
        Label:
            pos_hint:{"center_x": 0.5, "top":1.05}
            size_hint:0.4, 0.3
            bold: True
            text: "Finite Automata"
            font_size: 38
        Label:
            pos_hint:{"center_x": 0.5, "top":0.8}
            font_size: 0.0175 * root.width
            size_hint:0.2,0.15
            text: "Finite Automata (FA) is the simplest machine to recognize patterns.The finite automata or finite state machine is an abstract \nmachine which have five elements or tuple.  It has a set of states and rules for moving from one state to another but it \ndepends upon the applied input symbol. Basically it is an abstract model of digital computer. \n\nSwitch between the tabs to find the DFA and NFA"
        Label:
            text: "String Verfication"
            pos_hint:{"center_x": 0.5, "top":0.55}
            size_hint:0.1, 0.1
            font_size: 30
        Label:
            text: "Condition goes here"
            pos_hint:{"top":0.4,"x":0.05}
            size_hint:0.2,0.05
        TextInput:
            id: txt1
            hint_text:"Ex '00', '01'"
            pos_hint:{"top":0.4,"x":0.3}
            size_hint:0.3, 0.05
            on_text: root.process0()
            
        Label:
            text: "String"
            pos_hint:{"top":0.3,"x":0.05}
            size_hint:0.2,0.05
        TextInput:
            id: txt2
            hint_text:"Ex '0000','010101"
            pos_hint:{"top":0.3,"x":0.3}
            size_hint:0.3, 0.05
            on_text: root.process1()
        Button:
            text: "go"
            pos_hint:{"top":0.1,"center_x":0.5}
            size_hint:0.1, 0.075
            background_normal: 'OIPg.png'
            background_down: 'OIPy.png'
            on_release:
                root.display()

<Ndfa>:
    FloatLayout:
        TabbedPanel:
            size_hint: 1,1
            pos_hint: {'center_x': 0.5, 'center_y': 0.5}
            tab_width: 125
            do_default_tab: False
            TabbedPanelItem:
                text: 'DFA'
                FloatLayout:
                    Label:
                        pos_hint:{"center_x": 0.5, "top":1.05}
                        size_hint:0.4, 0.3
                        bold: True
                        text: "Deterministic Finite Automata"
                        font_size: 35
                    Label:
                        pos_hint:{"center_x": 0.5, "top":0.8}
                        font_size: 0.0175 * root.width
                        size_hint:0.2,0.15
                        text: "In DFA, for each input symbol, one can determine the state to which the machine will move. Hence, it is called Deterministic \nAutomaton. As it has a finite number of states, the machine is called Deterministic Finite Machine or Deterministic Finite\nAutomaton."
                    ToggleButton:
                        size_hint: None, None
                        size: 0.15 * root.width, 0.015 * root.height 
                        pos: 0.125 * root.width, 0.450 * root.height 
                        background_normal: 'OIPb.png'
                        background_down: 'OIPy.png'
                        text: "Starts with"
                        font_size: (root.width*2 + root.height*2) / 2**8
                        group: "NFA"
                        on_release:
                            root.active()
            
                    ToggleButton:
                        size_hint: None, None
                        size: 0.15 * root.width, 0.015 * root.height
                        pos: 0.435 * root.width, 0.450 * root.height 
                        group: "NFA"
                        background_normal: 'OIPb.png'
                        background_down: 'OIPy.png'
                        text: "Ends with"
                        font_size: (root.width*2 + root.height*2) / 2**8
                        on_release:
                            root.active()
                
                    ToggleButton:
                        size_hint: None, None
                        size: 0.15 * root.width, 0.015 * root.height
                        pos: 0.75 * root.width, 0.450 * root.height
                        background_normal: 'OIPb.png'
                        background_down: 'OIPy.png'
                        group: "NFA"
                        text: "In between"
                        font_size: (root.width*2 + root.height*2) / 2**8
                        on_release:
                            root.active()


            TabbedPanelItem:
                text: 'NFA'
                background_image: 'res5.jpg'
                FloatLayout:
                    Label:
                        pos_hint:{"center_x": 0.5, "top":1.05}
                        size_hint:0.4, 0.3
                        bold: True
                        text: "Non - Deterministic Finite Automata"
                        font_size: 35
                    Label:
                        pos_hint:{"center_x": 0.5, "top":0.8}
                        font_size: 0.0175 * root.width
                        size_hint:0.2,0.15
                        text: "In NDFA, for a particular input symbol, the machine can move to any combination of the states in the machine. In other words, the \nexact state to which the machine moves cannot be determined Hence, it is called Non-deterministic Automation.."
                
                    ToggleButton:
                        size_hint: None, None
                        size: 0.15 * root.width, 0.015 * root.height 
                        pos: 0.125 * root.width, 0.450 * root.height 
                        background_normal: 'OIPb.png'
                        background_down: 'OIPy.png'
                        text: "Starts with"
                        font_size: (root.width*2 + root.height*2) / 2**8
                        group: "NFA"
                        on_release:
                            root.active()
            
                    ToggleButton:
                        size_hint: None, None
                        size: 0.15 * root.width, 0.015 * root.height
                        pos: 0.435 * root.width, 0.450 * root.height 
                        group: "NFA"
                        background_normal: 'OIPb.png'
                        background_down: 'OIPy.png'
                        text: "Ends with"
                        font_size: (root.width*2 + root.height*2) / 2**8
                        on_release:
                            root.active()
                    
                    ToggleButton:
                        size_hint: None, None
                        size: 0.15 * root.width, 0.015 * root.height
                        pos: 0.75 * root.width, 0.450 * root.height
                        background_normal: 'OIPb.png'
                        background_down: 'OIPy.png'
                        group: "NFA"
                        text: "In between"
                        font_size: (root.width*2 + root.height*2) / 2**8
                        on_release:
                            root.active()
